author: Paulina Duran
title: New Zealand dollar up slightly, recovers losses made after RBNZ - Reuters
description: The New Zealand dollar recouped early losses made after the central bank delayed raising interest rates as the country entered a snap COVID-19 lockdown, while the Australian dollar also edged higher.
